cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.SY 

This paper deals with efficient grouping and resource allocation for multicast transmission in LTE networks, which involves aspects of networking (cs.NI), multimedia (cs.MM), optimization (cs.DS, cs.IT), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.NI and cs.MM, followed by cs.DS, cs.IT, and cs.SY.
